Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: A person sees a crowd gathered in a park. Wading through he sees a man playing chess with a dog. "What a smart dog" they exclaim. "Not really", replies a member of the crowd. "It's down two to five". This is basically how I feel when people discuss current AI abilities.
